---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Booking & Cancellation Policy"
  description="A full-page policy layout outlining booking requirements, payment terms, rescheduling and cancellation rules, weather contingencies, and location permit information for event bookings."
>
  <article class="container--narrow policy-article">
    <header class="policy-header">
      <span class="label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Booking & Cancellation Policy</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>1. Booking and Payment</h2>
      <p>
        To secure your preferred date and time, a 50% non-refundable retainer is
        required at the time of booking. The remaining balance must be paid in
        full at least 7 days prior to the event date. For bookings made less
        than 7 days in advance, full payment is required upfront.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>2. Rescheduling & Cancellations</h2>
      <p>
        We understand that plans can change. If you need to reschedule, please
        notify us at least 72 hours before your event.
      </p>
      <ul class="policy-list" role="list">
        <li class="policy-list__item">
          <span class="label">Rescheduling</span>
          <p>
            Your retainer can be transferred to a new date (subject to
            availability) within 90 days of the original booking.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="policy-list__item">
          <span class="label">Cancellations</span>
          <p>
            Cancellations made within 72 hours of the event are non-refundable.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>3. Weather Policy</h2>
      <p>
        The beauty of Hawaii comes with unpredictable weather. In the event of
        rain or high winds, you may reschedule for a future date at no
        additional cost.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>4. Locations & Permits</h2>
      <p>
        We operate in compliance with local regulations. Certain beaches or
        parks may require specific permits or have restrictions on group sizes.
        We will guide you through the best available locations during the
        booking process.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-article {
    padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--section-gap));
    padding-bottom: var(--section-gap);
  }

  .policy-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: calc(2 * var(--spacing));
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    margin-bottom: calc(3 * var(--spacing));
  }

  .policy-section {
    margin-bottom: calc(3 * var(--spacing));
  }

  .policy-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing);
  }

  .policy-section p {
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .policy-list {
    margin-top: calc(1.5 * var(--spacing));
    background-color: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
  }

  .policy-list__item {
    padding: calc(1.25 * var(--spacing)) calc(1.5 * var(--spacing));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .policy-list__item + .policy-list__item {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
  }
</style>
